title: no chest on ornn
body: I got an s rank on ornn but got no chest has anyone else had this problem :(

replies.body: I'm not currently seeing any S's with Ornn in your recent match history, but there's a chance that it could just be taking a little bit to update properly. Give it a bit of time, and if you still aren't seeing the chest shoot me a screenshot with that S and I should be able to get this straightened out!
